OL,3,CThe moment a spoon-wielding drug
OL,4,Caddict attempts to rob Post Office
OL,6,FCCTV footage shows the moment a man
OL,7,Fuses a spoon to try and steal cash
OL,8,Ffrom behind a post office counter...
OL,10,FA drug addict who attempted to steal a
OL,11,Fwad of cash from a Nottingham using a
OL,12,Fspoon has been sentenced.
OL,14,F36-year-old Jelanie Scott entered
OL,15,FHyson Green Post Office in Gregory
OL,16,FBoulevard at approximately 11.45am on
OL,17,FSaturday 10 February.
