OL,3,CThe moment a spoon-wielding drug
OL,4,Caddict attempts to rob Post Office
OL,6,FHe approached a counter window on
OL,7,Fcrutches before reaching through a
OL,8,Fsmall gap at the bottom with a large
OL,9,Fserving spoon.
OL,11,FStaff behind the screen quickly
OL,12,Fspotted his movement and activated the
OL,13,Fpanic alarm - which triggered the
OL,14,Fsecurity smoke system.
OL,16,FCCTV footage shows Scott, along with
OL,17,Fthree other customers, fleeing the
OL,18,Fshop through the cloud of smoke.
