OL,3,CThe moment a spoon-wielding drug
OL,4,Caddict attempts to rob Post Office
OL,6,FAs he left, Scott dropped a debit card
OL,7,Fwith his name on it before getting
OL,8,Finto a taxi.
OL,10,FPolice recognised him from CCTV
OL,11,Ffootage and he was arrested nine days
OL,12,Flater after patrolling officers
OL,13,Fspotted him in Forest Road West in
OL,14,FRadford.
OL,16,FScott of Leslie Road in Forest Fields
OL,17,Fadmitted the offence, telling officers
OL,18,Fhe had taken cocaine and heroin
OL,19,Fshortly before the incident, and that
OL,20,Fhe was suffering with his mental
OL,21,Fhealth.
