OL,3,CThe moment a spoon-wielding drug
OL,4,Caddict attempts to rob Post Office
OL,6,FHe was charged with attempted burglary
OL,7,Fand pleaded guilty at Nottingham
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,10,FScott was handed a community order
OL,11,Fcomprising a six-month drug
OL,12,Frehabilitation programme and was fined
OL,13,F#50, in addition to a #114 victim
OL,14,Fsurcharge and #85 court costs.
OL,16,FSergeant Mark Southgate, of the City
OL,17,FCentral neighbourhood policing team,
OL,18,Fsaid:
