OL,6,F"There was overwhelming evidence in
OL,7,Fthis case and I am pleased Scott has
OL,8,Fbeen held to account for his actions.
OL,10,F"He told officers it was a stupid
OL,11,Fthing to do and I hope he now reflects
OL,12,Fon his behaviour and stays out of
OL,13,Ftrouble."
